cudh and pydh high performance kernels for GPUs and CPUs
========================================================

code structure
--------------


PYDH

    Python module (pydh.py)

    Cython interface (c_pydh_interface.pyx)

    C++ library (c_pydh.cc)

    (.pyx and .cc are in the same compilation unit)


CUDH

    Python module (cudh.py)

    Cython interface (c_cudh_interface.pyx)

    C++ library (c_cudh.cu)

    (.pyx and .cu are in different compilation units)
